title: This working mom is Republicans' best shot at unseating Marjorie Taylor Greene -- if they want to - CNN
content: This working mom is Republicans' best shot at unseating Marjorie Taylor Greene -- if they want to  CNNView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Jennifer Strahan is taking on Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene in the Republican primary for Georgia's 14th District. But unlike in North Carolina, where Republicans mobilized to help defeat GOP Rep. Madison Cawthorn, Greene hasn't encountered the same level of organized opposition -- or spending -- against her.
